{color:#172b4d} The arrows between the status (e.g. "Open" to "In Progress)" in the "Activity" area in an issue view in the "Transition" tab are implemented without the alt attribute (see picture 2). "{color}
{color:#172b4d} → The icons must be provided with an <alt> attribute, which contains a descriptive and content-related alternative text.{color}
